title: It's Already Defeated | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: It's Already Defeated | Joel Osteen
description:
What you’re up against has already been defeated. Because you belong to God, nothing can keep you from His promises.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
